{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "8f1c0aa0-0000-4000-8000-report-service",
    "name": "report-service",
    "description": "Smoke + fixture collection for the report-service ingestion + admin read surface.\n\n**Auth**\n- SDK-facing endpoints (`/api/v1/*`, `/api/v2/*`): `apiKey` header (`{{apiKey}}`)\n- Admin endpoints (`/admin/api/*`, Razor pages): session cookie via DevAutoSignIn (Development only). Run the **Admin — sign in** request first; Postman stores the cookie automatically.\n\n**Import** cleanly into Postman, Bruno (`Import → Postman Collection`), Insomnia, and Hoppscotch — v2.1.0 Postman Collection format.\n\nEdit the `report-service · local` environment for a different host or apiKey.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "apikey",
    "apikey": [
      { "key": "key",   "value": "apiKey",       "type": "string" },
      { "key": "value", "value": "{{apiKey}}",   "type": "string" },
      { "key": "in",    "value": "header",        "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "pm.test('response is not 5xx', () => pm.expect(pm.response.code).to.be.lessThan(500));",
          "pm.test('response under 5s',   () => pm.expect(pm.response.responseTime).to.be.below(5000));"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
